Hey <%= @user.name.split.first %>,

<% case @urgency %>
<% when :day_before_quali %>
Qualifying for this weekend's race is TOMORROW! Don't miss your chance to lock in your predictions.
<% when :day_of_quali %>
Qualifying starts TODAY! Your qualifying predictions will lock when the session begins.
<% when :day_of_race %>
The race is TODAY! This is your final chance to make your podium and fastest lap predictions before they lock.
<% end %>

ROUND <%= @race.round %>: <%= @race.name.upcase %>
<%= @race.circuit_name %>, <%= @race.circuit_country %>
<% if @urgency == :day_of_race && @race.race_date %>
Race starts: <%= format_time_for_user(@race.race_date, @user_timezone) %>
<% elsif @race.quali_date %>
Qualifying: <%= format_time_for_user(@race.quali_date, @user_timezone) %>
<% end %>
<% if @race.has_sprint? %>
Sprint Weekend
<% end %>

Make your predictions now: <%= @predictions_url %>

Good luck! Remember, every correct prediction earns you points on the leaderboard.

